### ApiGateway JWT Authentication Test Dosyası

### 1. Login (Token almak için - Public endpoint)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Register (Kayıt olmak için - Public endpoint)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### 3. Korumalı endpoint testi - Token olmadan (401 Unauthorized beklenir)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/users/profile

### 4. Korumalı endpoint testi - Token ile (200 OK beklenir)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Portfolio endpoint testi - Token ile
GET https://localhost:5001/api/portfolios
